    {"id":"g-ops","type":"group","x":80,"y":260,"width":760,"height":440,"color":"2","label":"Operations"},

    {"id":"tn-hero","type":"text","x":1100,"y":260,"width":740,"height":440,"color":"6","text":"# Mesh Platform\n\nAI-native IDE. Two cooperating Azure App Service processes share a capsule-compressed workspace.\n\n---\n\n| Process | Role |\n|---------|------|\n| **Gateway** | HTTP, auth, UI, API surface |\n| **Worker** | Workspace ops, indexing, compression, git |\n| **Fanout** | Azure Function — capsule write-back |\n\n---\n\n`global.*` fully removed — all modules use explicit DI via `core` object."},

    {"id":"tn-browser","type":"text","x":-3040,"y":-860,"width":360,"height":540,"color":"5","text":"## Browser\n\n**REST** `/api/...`\n\n**WebSocket** `/terminal`\nReal pty shell via node-pty\n\n**WebSocket** `/api/realtime`\nPCM audio stream — VAD → STT → TTS\n\n---\n\nMonaco editor, file explorer, dependency graph, chat panel, voice surface"},

    {"id":"tn-gateway","type":"text","x":-1420,"y":-760,"width":860,"height":520,"color":"6","text":"## Gateway Responsibilities\n\n- Security headers · CSRF guard · Request IDs\n- JSON body limits (1 MB global / 200 MB ingest)\n- Structured JSON logger (`src/logger.js`)\n- Startup env-var validation (`src/core/startup-checks.js`)\n- Pre-built view route Map (no `fs.existsSync` on hot path)\n\n**Route factories receive `core` explicitly:**\n```\ncreateAuthRouter(core)\ncreateAppRouter(core)\ncreateAssistantRouter(core)\nsetupTerminalRelay(server, { projectRoot, core })\nsetupRealtimeRelay(server, core)\n```\n\n**Fallback strategy:** every workspace endpoint tries `meshTunnelRequest → Worker` first; falls back to local `src/core/index.js` if Worker is unreachable."},

    {"id":"tn-comp","type":"text","x":-160,"y":-640,"width":760,"height":400,"color":"4","text":"## Capsule Pipeline\n\n**rawStorage** → Brotli-9 sync (`brotli-base64`)\nLegacy: `deflate-base64`, `utf8-base64` still decoded\n\n**Transport chunks** → zstd (Node 22+) or Brotli q9 + LGWIN:22\n**Chunk size** → 256 KB\n\n**Tiers:** `ultra` · `medium` · `loose`\n\n**Token budget** (tiered by file size)\n≤500 → 60% · ≤2k → 40% · ≤8k → 25% · >8k → 15%\n\n**Focused scoring:** exact word-boundary match = 3×, substring = 1×"},

