    {"id":"d-cos2","type":"text","x":1940,"y":-620,"width":720,"height":520,"color":"1","text":"## Data Stores\n\n**Cosmos DB** — workspace metadata, capsule records, user store\n- `MESH_COSMOS_WORKSPACE_FILES_CONTAINER`\n- `MESH_COSMOS_WORKSPACES_CONTAINER`\n\n**Azure Blob** — raw file storage for upload workspaces\n- SAS tokens: upload · ingest · read · delete\n- `MESH_AZURE_OFFLOAD_ENABLED` gates blob mode\n\n**SQLite (encrypted)** — users, sessions, user-store\n- `MESH_SECURE_DB_FILE` → `/home/data/mesh-secure-v2.db`\n- `MESH_DATA_ENCRYPTION_KEY` — never rotate"},

    {"id":"dv-scr","type":"file","file":"Development/Scripts and Commands.md","x":-1420,"y":300,"width":340,"height":80},
    {"id":"dv-ccm","type":"file","file":"Development/ccmon Dashboard.md","x":-1060,"y":300,"width":340,"height":80},
    {"id":"dv-test","type":"file","file":"Development/Testing.md","x":-1420,"y":400,"width":340,"height":80},
    {"id":"dv-ccm2","type":"text","x":-1060,"y":400,"width":340,"height":280,"color":"3","text":"## ccmon\n\nClaude Code usage dashboard.\n\nAPI server: `http://localhost:3030`\nVite frontend: `http://localhost:5173`\n\n```bash\n# start API\nnode ccmon/server.js\n\n# start UI\ncd ccmon-web && npm run dev\n```"},

    {"id":"o-env","type":"file","file":"Operations/Environment Variables.md","x":100,"y":300,"width":340,"height":80},
    {"id":"o-dep","type":"file","file":"Operations/Deploy Runbook.md","x":460,"y":300,"width":340,"height":80},
    {"id":"o-trou","type":"file","file":"Operations/Troubleshooting.md","x":100,"y":400,"width":340,"height":80},
    {"id":"o-env2","type":"text","x":460,"y":400,"width":340,"height":280,"color":"2","text":"## Deploy\n\nAzure App Service — GitHub Actions CI\n\n```bash\naz webapp deploy \\\n  -g mesh-rg \\\n  -n mesh-gateway-303137 \\\n  --src-path dist.zip\n```\n\n`NODE_ENV=production` gates startup validation and disables demo user."}
